@startuml lowtalkers_escape-reality

actor User

participant "React Client" as Client
participant "Express Server" as Server
database "MariaDB" as DB
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "Wikipedia API" as WikiAPI

User -> Client: Interacts with VR scene
Client -> Server: API requests (auth, data)
Server -> DB: Query/update data
Server -> S3: Store/retrieve images
Server -> WikiAPI: Fetch article data

Client <-- Server: Response data
Server <-- DB: Query results
Server <-- S3: Image data
Server <-- WikiAPI: Article content

User <-- Client: Updated VR scene

@enduml